  "title": "Retail Operations Support (Admin Assistants) x 5 | Mon–Fri | Islandwide",
  "description": "<h2>💰 <strong>Salary & Work Details</strong></h2><p><strong>Gross Salary:</strong> $2,000 – $2,200 per month<br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, <strong>10:45am – 8:30pm</strong></p><p><strong>📍 Work Location in Bookstore: North, NorthEast, Central</strong></p><h2>📝 <strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Perform daily administrative functions for the retail store</p></li><li><p>Process SAP-related documents (invoice verification, goods receipt, data entry & filing)</p></li><li><p>Handle incoming phone calls and general office administration</p></li><li><p>Replenish office and housekeeping supplies</p></li><li><p>Assist in stocktaking activities</p></li><li><p>Support ad-hoc duties assigned by the Retail Manager</p></li></ul><h2>🎯 <strong>Job Requirements</strong></h2><p>🎓 Minimum <strong>2 years’ relevant experience</strong><br /><em>(Retail / hospitality experience is a PLUS!)</em><br />💻 Proficient in <strong>MS Office</strong><br />⚡ Able to thrive in a <strong>fast-paced environment</strong><br />⏰ Able to start work <strong>immediately or within short notice</strong><br /></p><p>📲 <strong>Apply Now!*</strong></p><p>WhatsApp us with <strong>RESUME to </strong><a href=\"tel:+65 8891 4996\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">+65 8891 4996</a></p><p><strong>Job Code: RAdmin</strong></p><p>----------------------------------------------------------------</p><p>*<em>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</em><br /><br />CREW by HRNet | HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd (24C2435)</p><p>Athirah Bte Rosli (R2197227)</p>",
